      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888;">
        <strong>Summary:</strong> Server mode: We collect only encrypted files (we can't decrypt them), optional email addresses for sharing, and ephemeral Ray IDs for debugging. P2P mode: Files never touch our servers—we only facilitate peer connections via signaling. We don't log IP addresses, don't track users, don't sell data, and automatically delete everything after expiration (24 hours for server mode, 5 minutes for P2P room data). Your privacy is our priority.
      </p>
